WEBVTT

00:01:26.836 --> 00:01:30.517
linked to al Qaeda.

00:01:30.517 --> 00:01:33.389
So how does the story of a small town kid

00:01:33.389 --> 00:01:35.210
just trying to make it big in the city

00:01:35.210 --> 00:01:38.040
end up with him blowing himself up?

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:40.012
He was waiting.

00:01:40.012 --> 00:01:41.910
He was waiting for an opportunity,

00:01:41.910 --> 00:01:43.692
waiting to begin his future,

00:01:43.692 --> 00:01:45.727
waiting for a way forward,

00:01:45.727 --> 00:01:48.106
and this was the first thing that came along.

00:01:48.106 --> 00:01:50.520
This was the first thing that pulled him out

00:01:50.520 --> 00:01:53.460
of what we call waithood.

00:01:53.460 --> 00:01:55.756
And his story repeats itself

00:01:55.756 --> 00:01:58.172
in urban centers around the world.

00:01:58.172 --> 00:02:00.926
It is the story of the disenfranchised,